instructions: Navigate to the last cell in the grid.
assertions: roleGrid gridBoundary nameTransactionsJanuary1ThroughJanuary6 numberColumns5 numberRows7 textLastColumnHeaderBalance textLastCell99553200 coordinatesLastCellColumn5Row7AreConveyed

title: Move focus forwards into a grid in reading mode
instructions: Move keyboard focus onto the first non-header cell in the grid.

title: Move focus backwards into a grid in reading mode
